# Cargo build artifacts — exclude at ANY depth. Plain `target` / `.cargo/target`
# only match the repo root; nested ones (apis/.cargo = 31G, scripts/.cargo = 12G,
# culex/src-tauri/target, …) need the **/ prefix or they get shipped in the context.
**/target
**/.cargo/target
**/.cargo/registry
**/.cargo/git
**/pkg

# Keep root .cargo/config.toml (sets the build target dir) — only the line above
# strips the heavy subdirs, the config file is still copied.

# Backup files generated by rustfmt
**/*.rs.bk

# node e2e test tools and outputs
**/node_modules
**/test-results
**/end2end/playwright-report
**/playwright/.cache
**/engine/flamegraph.svg
**/engine/log
**/engine/perf.data

# Workspace members are: apis, engine, db, shared_types, hive-hydra.
culex
chronos
scripts
busybee
dev-container

# Local dev state, logs, VCS
.git
.direnv
.pg
logs
*.log
fly.toml
